{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_RemoveForceField}}
'''A_RemoveForceField'''<br>
(no parameter)<br>

Removes the BLOCKING and BLOCKEVERYTHING flags from all two-sided [[linedefs]] with the [[ForceField]] special, clear their special, and removes their midtextures on both sides.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|DegninOre}}, {{Class|ForceFieldGuard}} and derived classes.

